Violet Kemble-Cooper https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Violet_Kemble-Cooper 0 Violet Kemble-Cooper (12 December 1886 – 17 August 1961) was an English-born stage and film actress, she emigrated to the USA in 1912, and appeared on stage and in Hollywood film.
